{>"partials/header" /}

{<title}Welcome{/title}

{<top}
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="col w-2-3 marg__bottom">
      <p class="hdr kilo no-marg-i"><span class="txt--blue">Target individuals.</span><br/> Not segments.</p>
      <p class="normal">When your website or application is powered by <strong>DADI</strong>, it adapts to create a better experience for your audience. We call this a <strong>Data Driven Experience</strong> – and we can help you build it.</p>
      <p class="normal pad__top"><a href="/solutions/" class="btn btn--blue">Learn how</a></p>
    </div>
    {@iter items=insights from=0 to=2}
      <div class="col w-1-3 {@eq key="{$idx}" value="1"}col--pull{/eq}">
        <p class="txt--grey hdr">{@formatDate data=attributes.date parseFormat="YYYY-DD-MMMTh:mm:ss.ZZ" format="Do MMMM" /}</p>
        <p class="hdr large txt--green"><a href="/insight/{handle}/">{attributes.title}</a></p>
        <p class="small">{@soberMarkdown}{@Truncate data="{attributes.preface}" length="110" ellipsis="true"/}{/soberMarkdown}</p>
        <p class="small"><a href="/insight/{handle}/" class="btn btn--green">Read more</a></p>
      </div>
    {/iter}
  </div>
{/top}

<div class="container container--pad">
  <div class="grid pad__bottom">
    <div class="col w-1-2 alignc">
    <img src="/assets/img/illo-dde.jpg" width="340">
    </div>
    <div class="col w-1-2">
      <p class="larger hdr txt--red">Data Driven Experiences</p>
      <p class="normal">The ability to process and understand user and environmental data in real time to provide a customised experience for the individual across multiple touch-points, improving engagement and optimising conversion.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{>"partials/content-modules/customers" /}

<div class="container container--divider">
  <p class="hdr larger">
    DADI is a ground up reimagination of web tech, built on a breakthrough thought:<br><br>
    <span class="txt--blue">It's all just data.</span>
  </p>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="col w-1-2">
      <p class="normal">The <strong>DADI</strong> platform enables the unification of disparate technologies by treating all content types in the same way, closing the gap between <em>WCM/ECM</em>, <em>CRM</em> and <em>DMP</em>, and making the implementation of cutting edge machine learning and big data theory simple.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col w-1-2">
      <p class="normal">With <strong>DADI</strong>, businesses of all sizes can provide data driven experience to their customers: unique and personalised interactions that drive higher engagement and increase conversion, all at a price point significantly below that of legacy platforms.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list--inline marg__bottom pad__top">
    <li><a href="/platform/" class="btn btn--blue normal">Learn how</a></li>
    <li><a href="/solutions/" class="btn btn--green normal">Solutions</a></li>
  </ul>
</div>

